{
  "id" : 782,
  "songNumber" : 170,
  "title" : "YOU HAVE HEARD OF LITTLE MOSES",
  "language" : "english",
  "capo" : 0,
  "bpm" : 0,
  "timeSignature" : "4/4",
  "hashtags" : [ ],
  "sections" : [ {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "Verse 1",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "You have heard of little Moses in the bulrush,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "You have heard of fearless David and his sling;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 41
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "You have heard the story told of dreaming Joseph,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 42
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And of Jonah and the whale you often sing.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 37
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "There are many, many others through the Bible,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 10
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "I should like to meet them all, I do declare !",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 39
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "By and by the Lord will surely let us meet them",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 38
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "At the meeting in the air.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 15
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 22
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "chorus",
    "label" : "Chorus",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "There is going to be a meeting in the air,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "In the sweet, sweet by and by;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 27
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "I am going to meet you, meet you there",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "In that home beyond the sky;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 8
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Such singing you will hear, never heard by mortal ear,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "'Twill be glorious, I do declare !",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 10
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 27
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And God's own Son will be the leading One",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 38
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "At the meeting in the air."
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "Verse 2",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "Many things will there be missing, in that meeting,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "For the mourners bench will have no place at all,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 45
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "There will never be a sermon preached to sinners,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 41
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "For the sinner had refused to heed the call.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 39
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "There will be no mourning over wayward loved ones,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 11
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "There will be no lonely nights of pleading prayer;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 11
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 43
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "All our burdens and our anguish will be lifted",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 40
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "At the meeting in the air."
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "Verse 3",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "There the doubters will be missing altogether,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 10
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "All the skeptics will be absent on that day;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 40
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "There will be no grumblers present to disturb us,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 41
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And the Achans will be busy far away.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 33
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "There the saints will have His \"seal upon their foreheads,\"",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 10
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Dressed in raiment none but ransomed ones can wear;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 11
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 46
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "All who have the wedding garments will be present",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 42
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "At the meeting in the air."
    } ]
  } ]
}